||              ||                                          ===============
(+==============+)
||              ||
 ================
 

 1, We connect mobile and PC via the network(or ADB, or Buletooth).
 2, Set the main key OR use default value.
 3, Start the game(like a sample car game, a sample plane game...) on PC.
 4, Use mobile's touch screen OR accelerometer.
 5, ...
 6, Enjoy it !
